name: MerryBananaMas 2020
description:
You've collected one of my artworks this year, thank you! Every time I see someone has nabbed one of my pieces, I do a lil big happy dance 💃

Merry Christmas to you if ya celebrate the day 😇. Merry Xmas to you if you celebrate the winter commercial activity season (😋). Have a super duper day If ya see the 25th as 'just another day' 🎉

Here's to a banana boat load of more amazing art in 2022 🥂
